  "content_markdown": "1\n\n###  Application and Definitions\n\n1.1\n\nUnless otherwise stated, this Part applies to every _firm_.\n\n*Effective: 31/12/2020*\n\n1.2\n\nIn this Part, the following definitions shall apply:\n\nhas the meaning given in _threshold condition_ 5F(3) (Effective Supervision).\n\nmeans the form referred to at [5.3.](/pra-rules/close-links#812c1f19864e4319a0ef4faff55f90a3 \"5.3.\")\n\nmeans the form referred to at [5.2](/pra-rules/close-links#e141f9b5ebeb49e2a906280bb16d844d \"5.2\").\n\nmeans the form referred to at [5.1](/pra-rules/close-links#962d4870ab4e4f1d82d13ef8574df019 \"5.1\").\n\n*Effective: 03/08/2015*\n\n2\n\n###  Requirement to Notify Changes in Close Links\n\n2.1\n\nA _firm_ must notify (or procure that another _firm_ in its _group_ notifies) the _PRA_ that it has begun to have or ceased to have _close links_ with any _person_.\n\n*Effective: 03/08/2015*\n\n2.2\n\nWhere a _firm_ has elected to report changes in _close links_ on a monthly basis under [3.1](/pra-rules/close-links#f9ece5add48c45fdb0aa4823b39ffd4a \"3.1\"), it must:\n\n  1. (1) within fifteen _business days_ of the end of each month, report (or procure that another _firm_ in its _group_ reports) electronically for that month, by completing the _Close Links Monthly Report _and submitting it through the relevant platform provided by the _PRA_ ;\n  2. (2) on a quarterly basis, submit (or procure that another _firm_ in its _group_ submits) a _group_ organisation chart, unless there have been no changes since the submission of the previous organisation chart to the _PRA_ , in which case the _group_ organisation chart is not required.\n\n*Effective: 03/08/2015*\n\n2.3\n\nThe _Close Links Monthly Report_ must include the information specified in the form.\n\n*Effective: 03/08/2015*\n\n2.4\n\nWhere a _firm_ has not elected to report changes in _close links_ on a monthly basis under [3.1](/pra-rules/close-links#f9ece5add48c45fdb0aa4823b39ffd4a \"3.1\"), it must make (or procure that another _firm_ in its _group_ makes) a notification by completing the _Close Links Notification Form_ as soon as reasonably practicable and no later than one month after it becomes aware that it has begun to have or ceased to have _close links_ with any person.\n\n*Effective: 03/08/2015*\n\n2.5\n\nThe notification submitted under [2.4](/pra-rules/close-links#5cbd40f04a624d668f160440c3ae1c3d \"2.4\") must be made by completing the _Close Links Notification Form_ and must include all the relevant information specified therein.\n\n*Effective: 03/08/2015*\n\n3\n\n###  Election to Notify Changes in Close Links on a Monthly Basis\n\n3.1\n\nA _firm_ wishing to report changes in _close links_ on a monthly basis must send a written notice of election to the _firm’s_ usual supervisory contact at the _PRA_.\n\n*Effective: 03/08/2015*\n\n3.2\n\nA firm wishing to cease reporting changes in _close links_ on a monthly basis must send a written notice of that intention to its usual supervisory contact at the _PRA_ at least one month before changing its _close links_ reporting practice.\n\n*Effective: 03/08/2015*\n\n4\n\n###  Annual Close Links Report\n\n4.1\n\nA _firm_ must submit (or procure that another _firm_ in its _group_ submits) annually by electronic means to the _PRA_ the _Close Links Annual Report_ , within four months of the _firm’s_ _accounting reference date_.\n\n*Effective: 03/08/2015*\n\n4.2\n\nAn unincorporated _friendly society_ is only required to submit a report under [4.1](/pra-rules/close-links#e5154d4df3074a2d88eff715efe192cb \"4.1\") if it is aware that it has _close links_.\n\n*Effective: 03/08/2015*\n\n4.3\n\nThe _Close Links Annual Report_ must include the information specified in the form.\n\n*Effective: 03/08/2015*\n\n5\n\n###  Forms\n\n5.1\n\nThe _Close Links Notification Form_ can be found [here](https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/-/media/boe/files/prudential-regulation/regulatory-reporting/banking/close-links-notification-form-dec18.xls \"Close Links Notification Form\").\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2019*\n\n5.2\n\nThe _Close Links Monthly Report_ can be found [here](https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/-/media/boe/files/prudential-regulation/regulatory-reporting/banking/rep001atemplatedec18.pdf \"Close Links Monthly Report\").\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2019*\n\n5.3\n\nThe _Close Links Annual Report_ can be found [here](https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/-/media/boe/files/prudential-regulation/regulatory-reporting/banking/rep001templatedec18.pdf \"Close Links Annual Report\").\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2019*",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"col9\">\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"part-content\">\n\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"8c9fc15f146f4475aabfb9c7cba14f41\" id=\"886fb9a1cfa14d6db704bb1a91dc5e84\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tApplication and Definitions\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"5ba8e8fd78d044ad976f55d09e03b674\" id=\"86e1659e6e044d9f840ec308b9894233\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>Unless otherwise stated, this Part applies to every<em> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/close-links/03-08-2015#86e1659e6e044d9f840ec308b9894233\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.1 before 31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"37ed9fdbaf484e54836ced9444276095\" id=\"32f31432dde14494b9be8b23523cc5d2\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>In this Part, the following definitions shall apply:</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">has the meaning given in <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66905\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-5fe3a4c616664511a625a0cddd8fbf72\" title=\"threshold condition\">threshold condition</a></em> 5F(3) (Effective Supervision).</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means the form referred to at <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/close-links#812c1f19864e4319a0ef4faff55f90a3\" title=\"5.3.\">5.3.</a></p>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means the form referred to at <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/close-links#e141f9b5ebeb49e2a906280bb16d844d\" title=\"5.2\">5.2</a>.</p>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means the form referred to at <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/close-links#962d4870ab4e4f1d82d13ef8574df019\" title=\"5.1\">5.1</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/08/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"9a796aeb3ca1404fbdb7a8771f51f87a\" id=\"c2227e1870914f65a1dd027fd88b404e\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t2\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tRequirement to Notify Changes in Close Links\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"da378ff434444f2db81474822dbc0678\" id=\"0ff4bb4deb0c4e8f856fbf763e6f1b92\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must notify (or procure that another <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> in its <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66903\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7fac9db6c44944108dd0d6e4aadc15d5\" title=\"group\">group</a></em> notifies) the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> that it has begun to have or ceased to have <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66906\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-611ddc69750244a4b3fe048897797549\" title=\"close links\">close links</a></em> with any <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66904\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-35605c24207b4a1b9a088beaf55f08ef\" title=\"person\">person</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/08/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"e43226878b1d477eb77ff1ac510db676\" id=\"307cae09bbb44e04abcdc658b4413171\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>Where a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> has elected to report changes in <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66906\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-611ddc69750244a4b3fe048897797549\" title=\"close links\">close links</a></em> on a monthly basis under <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/close-links#f9ece5add48c45fdb0aa4823b39ffd4a\" title=\"3.1\">3.1</a>, it must:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) within fifteen <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52213\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-0ac6fe17ff7f43e08f14112960b50c73\" title=\"business days\">business days</a></em> of the end of each month, report (or procure that another <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> in its <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66903\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7fac9db6c44944108dd0d6e4aadc15d5\" title=\"group\">group</a></em> reports) electronically for that month, by completing the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66908\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-083e884a8a1f41f78252e7b9e3923bce\" title=\"Close Links Monthly Report \">Close Links Monthly Report</a> </em>and submitting it through the relevant platform provided by the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em>;</li>\n<li>(2) on a quarterly basis, submit (or procure that another <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> in its <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66903\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7fac9db6c44944108dd0d6e4aadc15d5\" title=\"group \">group </a></em>submits) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66903\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7fac9db6c44944108dd0d6e4aadc15d5\" title=\"group\">group</a></em> organisation chart, unless there have been no changes since the submission of the previous organisation chart to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em>, in which case the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66903\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7fac9db6c44944108dd0d6e4aadc15d5\" title=\"group\">group</a></em> organisation chart is not required.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/08/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"89afb429deda447b97a5284f14824851\" id=\"09b629d677164d548f262770b6f4b46b\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66908\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-083e884a8a1f41f78252e7b9e3923bce\" title=\"Close Links Monthly Report\">Close Links Monthly Report</a></em> must include the information specified in the form.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/08/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"3d465a53b8d74ff9a8464de2e57ce564\" id=\"5cbd40f04a624d668f160440c3ae1c3d\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.4\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>Where a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> has not elected to report changes in <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66906\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-611ddc69750244a4b3fe048897797549\" title=\"close links\">close links</a></em> on a monthly basis under <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/close-links#f9ece5add48c45fdb0aa4823b39ffd4a\" title=\"3.1\">3.1</a>, it must make (or procure that another <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> in its <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66903\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7fac9db6c44944108dd0d6e4aadc15d5\" title=\"group\">group</a></em> makes) a notification by completing the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66909\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-23d30896d4744435aefd1b7d50ac5871\" title=\"Close Links Notification Form\">Close Links Notification Form</a></em> as soon as reasonably practicable and no later than one month after it becomes aware that it has begun to have or ceased to have <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66906\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-611ddc69750244a4b3fe048897797549\" title=\"close links\">close links</a></em> with any person.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/08/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"f12ea9702ada45858af263e097e36308\" id=\"81515dab812a43748bc874299eca5017\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.5\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The notification submitted under <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/close-links#5cbd40f04a624d668f160440c3ae1c3d\" title=\"2.4\">2.4</a> must be made by completing the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66909\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-23d30896d4744435aefd1b7d50ac5871\" title=\"Close Links Notification Form\">Close Links Notification Form</a></em> and must include all the relevant information specified therein.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/08/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"e1f49a9db39c408c810471cc0a47f04a\" id=\"7345df6d88c541958d2ab918e75227a5\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t3\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tElection to Notify Changes in Close Links on a Monthly Basis\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"00a28d05d2084db89d5672c085b4cd12\" id=\"f9ece5add48c45fdb0aa4823b39ffd4a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> wishing to report changes in <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66906\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-611ddc69750244a4b3fe048897797549\" title=\"close links\">close links</a></em> on a monthly basis must send a written notice of election to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm’s\">firm’s</a></em> usual supervisory contact at the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/08/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"c17373561e5d4f0094844b331d3d2f70\" id=\"d1667d3894bf42babb2bbea4a63b64f1\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A firm wishing to cease reporting changes in <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66906\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-611ddc69750244a4b3fe048897797549\" title=\"close links\">close links</a></em> on a monthly basis must send a written notice of that intention to its usual supervisory contact at the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> at least one month before changing its <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66906\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-611ddc69750244a4b3fe048897797549\" title=\"close links\">close links</a></em> reporting practice.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/08/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"845703c8692141388d12adad27cacd7c\" id=\"3fc2607ab83241898ae841ca50acd838\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t4\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tAnnual Close Links Report\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"84c92fb959234f18938e4c886d8e3d87\" id=\"e5154d4df3074a2d88eff715efe192cb\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must submit (or procure that another<em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\" firm\"> firm</a></em> in its <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66903\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-7fac9db6c44944108dd0d6e4aadc15d5\" title=\"group\">group</a></em> submits) annually by electronic means to the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52117\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-494fbb81077e408f84519b8c66998fef\" title=\"PRA\">PRA</a></em> the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66907\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-2d9accf081d94522936ac7945fffb8d2\" title=\"Close Links Annual Report\">Close Links Annual Report</a></em>, within four months of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm’s\">firm’s</a></em> <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"53195\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-90796708e59b4bc7b03bf3130c082b17\" title=\"accounting reference date\">accounting reference date</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/08/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"9670cbdd56a0469e86816862a6a0e03a\" id=\"0cfeab5ccfd84760a213ce15e147aa1e\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>An unincorporated <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66902\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-2d9041b9715141809ac1fcf70b9dcdeb\" title=\"friendly society\">friendly society</a></em> is only required to submit a report under <a data-mce-contenttype=\"7\" data-mce-linktype=\"1\" data-rb-content-link=\"Rule\" href=\"/pra-rules/close-links#e5154d4df3074a2d88eff715efe192cb\" title=\"4.1\">4.1</a> if it is aware that it has <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66906\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-611ddc69750244a4b3fe048897797549\" title=\"close links\">close links</a></em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/08/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"22d122bc991840e1899d9be69ea36509\" id=\"5aba5294f4044ebfa93f68f6bb59e4cd\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.3\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66907\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-2d9accf081d94522936ac7945fffb8d2\" title=\"Close Links Annual Report\">Close Links Annual Report</a></em> must include the information specified in the form.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t03/08/2015\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"701d0dd02953444189c8aee2750750a9\" id=\"4875c747b2854dc0a9a29ba6b2bc4bcf\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t5\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tForms\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"9fb8af4d4ed74009bc75784688199af0\" id=\"962d4870ab4e4f1d82d13ef8574df019\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t5.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>The <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"66909\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-23d30896d4744435aefd1b7d50ac5871\" title=\"Close Links Notification Form\">Close Links Notification Form</a></em> can be found <a class=\"external-link\" data-mce-description=\"Application to submit a notification of a close link\" data-mce-externalform=\"true\" data-mce-linktype=\"4\" href=\"https://www.bankofengland.co.uk/-/media/boe/files/prudential-regulation/regulatory-reporting/banking/close-links-notification-form-dec18.xls\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Close Link